Application Description:
	This is an app links the skills with skillsection and classes 



Usage:
	Either Enter : python -m flask run 
	       Or    : python runserver
	       

Please Note:
       1. Since I used a template inherinetion The page can not refresh automatically if you save the skill. However, click on "Go To Main Page"












Heroku Address: https://git.heroku.com/a634.git



Testing: Please create a database called "hushizh_testdb" on local to use the test

To run type: python a634_test.py in the command line

